title: Volvo car sales in Sweden 2009 to 2019
summary: In general Units sold has rose over the Year.
Units sold is slightly increasing from 2014 to 2015, and finally roughly constant from 2015 to 2016.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum Units sold, about 71238.0 was reported at Year 2016
The lowest Units sold, of value 61496.0 was reported at Year 2014
